    "Sunshine": "陽光",
    "A LizardByte project": "LizardByte 專案",
    "Sunshine is a self-hosted game stream host for Moonlight. Offering low latency, cloud gaming\nserver capabilities with support for AMD, Intel, and Nvidia GPUs for hardware encoding. Software\nencoding is also available. You can connect to Sunshine from any Moonlight client on a variety\nof devices. A web UI is provided to allow configuration, and client pairing, from your favorite\nweb browser. Pair from the local server or any mobile device.": "Sunshine 是 Moonlight 的自助遊戲串流主機。提供低延遲、雲端遊戲\n伺服器功能，支援 AMD、Intel 和 Nvidia GPU 的硬體編碼。軟體\n編碼也可用。您可以從各種\n裝置上的任何 Moonlight 用戶端連接至 Sunshine。提供的 Web UI 允許從您喜愛的\nWeb 瀏覽器進行配置和用戶端配對。從本機伺服器或任何行動裝置進行配對。",
    "Features": "特點",
    "Self-hosted": "自行託管",
    "Run Sunshine on your own hardware. No need to pay monthly fees to a\ncloud gaming provider.": "在您自己的硬體上執行 Sunshine。無需向\n雲端遊戲供應商支付月費。",
    "Moonlight": "月光",
    "Moonlight Support": "月光支援",
    "Connect to Sunshine from any Moonlight client. Moonlight is available\nfor Windows, macOS, Linux, Android, iOS, Xbox, and more. See": "從任何 Moonlight 客戶端連接至 Sunshine。Moonlight 適用於\nWindows、macOS、Linux、Android、iOS、Xbox 等平台。查看",
    "clients": "客戶",
    "for more information.": "以獲得更多資訊。",
    "Hardware Encoding": "硬體編碼",
    "Sunshine supports AMD, Intel, and Nvidia GPUs for hardware encoding.\nSoftware encoding is also available.": "Sunshine 支援 AMD、Intel 及 Nvidia GPU 進行硬體編碼。\n也可使用軟體編碼。",
    "Low Latency": "低延遲",
    "Sunshine is designed to provide the lowest latency possible to achieve optimal gaming performance.": "Sunshine 旨在提供最低的延遲時間，以達到最佳的遊戲效能。",
    "Control": "控制",
    "Sunshine emulates an Xbox, PlayStation, or Nintendo Switch controller.\nUse nearly any controller on your Moonlight client!": "Sunshine 可模擬 Xbox、PlayStation 或 Nintendo Switch 控制器。\n在 Moonlight 客戶端上使用幾乎任何控制器！",
